// MARK: - Tips & FAQ Long Descriptions (Investment)

"Start investing early through SIPs to benefit from the power of compounding. Even small monthly amounts grow significantly over long periods." = "通过定投尽早开始投资，享受复利的力量。即使每月少量投入，长期也能显著增长。";
"Compare lump sum vs SIP investment strategies. SIPs help average out market volatility through rupee cost averaging." = "比较一次性投资与定投策略。定投通过成本平均法帮助平滑市场波动。";
"Keep a portion of your portfolio in Fixed Deposits for capital safety and guaranteed returns, especially for short-term goals." = "将投资组合的一部分放在定期存款中，确保资本安全和保证收益，特别适合短期目标。";
"Recurring Deposits help build financial discipline. Automate monthly savings to build a corpus over time." = "定期储蓄有助于培养财务纪律。自动化每月储蓄，随时间积累资金。";
"Use a Systematic Withdrawal Plan (SWP) to generate regular retirement income from your mutual fund investments." = "使用系统化提取计划从基金投资中获得定期退休收入。";
"Maximize your NPS contributions to get additional tax deductions under Section 80CCD(1B), over and above the 80C limit." = "最大化您的 NPS 缴款，在第 80CCD(1B) 条下获得额外税收减免，超出 80C 限额。";
"Track your Provident Fund balance regularly to plan for retirement. PF offers guaranteed returns with tax benefits." = "定期追踪您的公积金余额以规划退休。公积金提供有税收优惠的保证收益。";

// MARK: - Tips & FAQ Long Descriptions (Loans)

"Try to maximize your down payment when taking a home loan. A higher down payment means lower EMIs and less interest paid overall." = "申请住房贷款时尽量增加首付。首付越高，每月分期越低，总利息越少。";
"Make prepayments on your home loan whenever possible. Even small additional payments can significantly reduce your total interest outgo." = "尽可能提前还款。即使少量额外还款也能显著减少总利息支出。";
"Avoid high-interest personal loans and credit card debt. Always compare interest rates and prefer secured loans for lower rates." = "避免高息个人贷款和信用卡债务。始终比较利率，优先选择有担保贷款以获得更低利率。";
"No-cost EMI schemes often include hidden charges or inflated product prices. Always compare the total cost before opting for such plans." = "零成本分期方案通常包含隐藏费用或虚高价格。选择前请务必比较总成本。";
"Always pay interest during the moratorium period of education loans. This prevents interest capitalization and reduces your total repayment." = "教育贷款延期期间务必支付利息。这可以防止利息资本化并减少总还款额。";
"Loan Against Property (LAP) typically offers lower interest rates than personal loans. Use it wisely for business or large expenses." = "房产抵押贷款通常比个人贷款利率更低。合理利用它来满足商业或大额支出需求。";
"Understand the Loan-to-Value (LTV) ratio for gold loans. Lenders typically offer 75% of the gold's market value." = "了解黄金贷款的贷款价值比。贷款机构通常提供黄金市值的 75%。";

// MARK: - Tips & FAQ Long Descriptions (Tax)

"Compare both Old and New tax regimes using the calculator. The best regime depends on your deductions and exemptions." = "使用计算器比较新旧两种税制。最佳税制取决于您的扣除和免税额。";
"Know your gratuity entitlement after 5 years of service. Gratuity is calculated based on your last drawn salary and years of service." = "了解服务 5 年后的退休金权益。退休金根据最后薪资和服务年限计算。";

// MARK: - About / Feature Descriptions

"All calculations run locally on your device. No data is collected, stored, or shared with any server." = "所有计算在设备本地运行。不会收集、存储或与任何服务器共享数据。";
"Your financial data is protected with automatic privacy screen when the app goes to background." = "应用进入后台时，自动隐私屏幕保护您的财务数据。";
"Track your daily expenses with custom categories, monthly summaries, and yearly graphical overviews." = "通过自定义类别、月度摘要和年度图表概览追踪日常支出。";
"Monitor your monthly outflows including EMIs, subscriptions, and recurring payments in one place." = "在一处监控您的月度支出，包括分期付款、订阅和定期付款。";
"Create and organize notes with rich text formatting, custom colors, and font styles." = "创建和整理带有富文本格式、自定义颜色和字体样式的笔记。";
"Export your financial reports as PDF or CSV files for record keeping and analysis." = "将财务报告导出为 PDF 或 CSV 文件，用于记录保存和分析。";
"Save calculator results for future reference and compare different scenarios side by side." = "保存计算结果以备将来参考，并排比较不同方案。";
"Support for multiple currencies to suit users across different regions." = "支持多种货币，适合不同地区的用户。";
"Personalised setup experience to customize the app for your financial needs." = "个性化设置体验，根据您的财务需求自定义应用。";
"Input validation ensures accurate calculations every time." = "输入验证确保每次计算准确无误。";
"Seamlessly adapts to light and dark mode for comfortable viewing." = "无缝适配浅色和深色模式，带来舒适的阅读体验。";

// MARK: - App Features Tips

"On first launch, a welcome screen lets you set your name, age, and preferred currency — so everything is ready from the start." = "首次启动时，欢迎界面让您设置姓名、年龄和首选货币 — 一切从一开始就准备就绪。";
"Your app can follow your device's language or you can pick a specific language from Settings — the entire UI updates instantly." = "应用可以跟随设备语言，也可以在设置中选择特定语言 — 整个界面即时更新。";
"Switch between INR, USD, EUR and more at any time. All calculators, expenses, and reports reflect your chosen currency symbol." = "随时切换 INR、USD、EUR 等货币。所有计算器、支出和报告都反映您选择的货币符号。";
"Toggle dark mode from Settings, or let the app follow your device's appearance for comfortable viewing day and night." = "在设置中切换深色模式，或让应用跟随设备外观，日夜舒适浏览。";
"Mark any calculator as a favourite and it appears in a dedicated Favourites section for one-tap access." = "将任何计算器标记为收藏，它会出现在专用收藏栏中，一键访问。";
"After computing a result, tap Save to store it. View or export all saved results later from the Saved section." = "计算结果后，点击保存。稍后从已保存栏查看或导出所有保存的结果。";
"Create colour-coded notes with adjustable font size, bold/italic styling, and a live Markdown preview." = "创建带颜色标记的笔记，支持调整字体大小、粗体/斜体样式和实时 Markdown 预览。";
"Export any expense or outflow report as a formatted PDF or a spreadsheet-ready CSV — great for record-keeping." = "将任何支出报告导出为格式化的 PDF 或可用于电子表格的 CSV — 非常适合记录保存。";

// MARK: - Expenses & Outflow Tips

"Log daily expenses under built-in or custom categories. Monthly totals and category splits update in real time." = "在内置或自定义类别下记录日常支出。月度总计和类别分类实时更新。";
"Add any category name you need — type it in the 'Other' field and it's saved automatically for future entries." = "添加您需要的任何类别名称 — 在「其他」字段中输入，自动保存供以后使用。";
"Swipe left on any expense or outflow row to quickly edit or delete it." = "在任何支出行左滑可快速编辑或删除。";
"Track EMIs, subscriptions, credit-card bills, and other fixed monthly commitments separately from daily expenses." = "将分期付款、订阅、信用卡账单和其他固定月度承诺与日常支出分开追踪。";
